title: Hour 2: Down a Buc
description:
Chris Canty, Harry Douglas and Damien Woody join the show to react to the news that Tampa Bay Buccaneers Pro-Bowl center Ryan Jensen will be out for months. The crew also debates which team they like best in the NFC. Later the crew debates if Kyler Murray is primed for a big year, and if Aaron Rodgers should play in the preseason.
